                 data-ratio='0.7'
                 itemprop="url"/>
          </div>
          <div class="rad-caption">
  <div class="rad-caption-wrapper">
    <span class="rad-caption-text">Here, we see the Marines carrying the injured man to the tank on the white wooden door. From this angle, we can see that the wounded Marine’s trousers have been loosened and pulled down to give access to the lower-back exit wound.</span>
